2022-08-15  Kjell Ahlstedt  <kjellahlstedt@gmail.com>

  docs: Don't translate GDK_MODIFIER_MASK to C++

  It's a preprocessor macro. It does not have a C++ name.
  Fixes #124

2022-08-04  Kjell Ahlstedt  <kjellahlstedt@gmail.com>

  4.7.1

